title: Clay Travis and Buck Sexton Show H1 – May 3 2022
itunes:title: Clay Travis and Buck Sexton Show H1 – May 3 2022
description:
On Clay's final day away, Buck tackles the abortion story about momentous SCOTUS leak from all angles. Buck says, "There's no constitutional right to abortion. This was a huge, monstrous lie, an obvious lie." Biden's total BS statement on abortion. If you believe it, you are getting your legal analysis, Buck reminds, from "the bottom of the Syracuse law school class of 1960-whatever." Fox's Shannon Bream joins Buck to update us on the unprecedented SCOTUS breach. Schumer vows abortion rights vote, reframes election. Clay and Buck predicted ploys like this would be coming. Dershowitz's theory on the leak. Don't be so sure the abortion decision won't change. Clay and Buck's predictions on the abortion decision.

Follow Clay & Buck on YouTube: https://www.youtube.com/c/clayandbuck
